Package org.usfirst.frc.team1699.robot.swerve

Classes for running a swerve drive system.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SwerveDrive
    Drive code, similar to RobotDrive, except for swerve drive robots.
    SwerveModule
    A class that represents a swerve module.
    SwerveUpdateRunnable
    Updates the PID loops of some SwerveModule objects.
    SwerveUpdateService
    A service that updates SwerveModule objects at a set interval or individually
    SwerveUpdateThread Deprecated
    Vector
    A number that has a magnitude (value) and direction (angle).
